{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1557,"date":"2022-04-13T08:28:59","date_gmt":"2022-04-13T08:28:59","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1557"},"modified":"2022-06-27T06:41:44","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T06:41:44","slug":"dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Dawn theme: vertical thumbnails with arrows for the product page images"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Shortly after the release of the Online Store 2.0, which was basically Shopify&#8217;s excellent update to the overall usability and user experience of the Customize page, the Dawn theme was made available for the public gaining some notoriously positive feedback. <br><br>It is no wonder though: with its elegant, modern design, and a &#8220;jQuery-less&#8221; component-based architecture implemented, the Dawn theme offers a much more performant website suitable for most types of businesses.<br><br>Anyhow, as with pretty much any other theme out there, there is still room for improvement, especially on the product page. The most obvious updates that are often discussed and requested are:<br><br>&#8211; vertical thumbnails;<br>&#8211; arrows;<br>&#8211; loop images;<br>&#8211; dots; <br>&#8211; sync swatches when images change (and vice-versa).<br><br>More importantly, while these updates can be nice, just hard coding them into the theme and having it permanently stuck there would not be of great use. <br><br>Being able to enable/disable these features to effortlessly A/B test and see what works better for the businesses is actually the ideal scenario.<br><br>Therefore, today I&#8217;ll teach you how you can add these features (plus a lot more customizable options) just by pasting one piece of code. The best part is that: <strong>customizations will not be overwritten</strong>. If you have any custom code, it will still be there afterward! Also, you don&#8217;t need any coding experience to do this.<br><br><a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview</a> of what the end result will look like. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/dawn-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Download </strong>the files by clicking here.</a> (<a href=\"https://pandashopdeals.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-adding-the-top-code\">Step 1: adding the &#8220;top&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /></li><li>Type the following on the search bar:<br><br><strong>main-product.liquid</strong><br><br>And open the file that is found. <br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"872\" height=\"632\" class=\"wp-image-1562\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg 872w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-850x616.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-768x557.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px\" /></li><li>Inside the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>top.txt</strong>. Copy all the code inside of this file.</li><li>Paste the code at the beginning of your <strong>main-product.liquid</strong> file, as the image indicates. <br><br>Before:<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1092\" height=\"642\" class=\"wp-image-1566\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg 1092w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-850x500.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1092px) 100vw, 1092px\" /><br><br>After:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"913\" height=\"755\" class=\"wp-image-1564\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3.jpg 913w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3-850x703.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-3-768x635.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 913px) 100vw, 913px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 2: adding the &#8220;bottom&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Still inside the &#8220;main-product.liquid&#8221; file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>{% schema</strong><br><br>Make sure you include the space after %.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1277\" height=\"733\" class=\"wp-image-1568\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg 1277w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-850x488.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-1200x689.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" /><br></li><li>Now, delete everything <strong>below </strong>the {% schema %} line, including the {% schema %}.<strong> </strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"730\" class=\"wp-image-1570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg 1134w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px\" /></li><li>Inside the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>bottom.txt</strong>. <br><br>Copy all the code inside of this file and paste it at the very bottom of the file.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1364\" height=\"728\" class=\"wp-image-1572\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6.jpg 1364w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-850x454.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-1200x640.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-6-768x410.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1364px) 100vw, 1364px\" /></li><li>That is it! </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-final-step-activating-and-customizing-the-slider\">Final step: activating and customizing the slider</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>><strong>Customize</strong>. Choose the theme that you just added the code to.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>At the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>Products</strong>> <strong>default product</strong>. <br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1154\" height=\"462\" class=\"wp-image-1577\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7.jpg 1154w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7-850x340.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-7-768x307.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1154px) 100vw, 1154px\" /></li><li>Once this page loads, click on <strong>Product Information</strong> on the left.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1145\" height=\"587\" class=\"wp-image-1581\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8.jpg 1145w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8-850x436.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-8-768x394.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1145px) 100vw, 1145px\" /></li><li>Scroll down to <strong>Media </strong>and activate whatever option you&#8217;d like. In this case, we&#8217;ll enable the vertical thumbnails:</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"381\" height=\"774\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1641\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-something-went-wrong-there-is-a-bug-or-i-can-t-install-it\">Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Just please send us an email to <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Take your Dawn theme product page to the premium level by adding arrows, image loop, dots and much more customization options. </p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1591,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[435],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-1-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-1-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/title-above-1-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Dawn Theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ti